# 🧠 Notes App (Full Stack)

A full-stack Notes application that allows users to securely create, view, and manage personal notes.
Built as part of a hands-on learning journey to move from tutorial-based learning to real-world application development.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 🔐 Authentication

- User signup with email and password
- Secure login with JWT (JSON Web Tokens)
- Password hashing using bcrypt
- Protected routes for authenticated users only

### 📝 Notes Management

- Create notes
- View all personal notes
- Delete notes
- Each user only accesses their own data

### 🌐 Frontend

- React-based UI
- API integration with backend
- Basic responsive styling using Tailwind CSS

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

### Frontend

- React
- Axios
- Tailwind CSS

### Backend

- Node.js
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL

### Authentication

- JWT (jsonwebtoken)
- bcrypt

---

