## 🎯 Learning Goals

This project was built to:

- Reinforce full-stack development skills
- Practice building without tutorials
- Understand authentication deeply
- Improve debugging and problem-solving

---

## 🧠 Key Takeaways

- Building > Watching tutorials
- Struggling = Learning
- Authentication is core to real applications
- Debugging is a primary skill

